# Backend API Deprecation Plan
# Full removal of api.tinyhumans.ai / staging-api.tinyhumans.ai surface
# Generated: 2026-05-21

---

## Scope decision

billing/, referral/, team/ and all backend-proxy modules are **fully removed with no replacement**.
This is a single-user local desktop. There is no subscription, no credit balance, no team, no
referral programme. The UI surfaces for those features are deleted too.

Channel delivery (Telegram, Discord, Slack, etc.) already has a fully native path in
`channels/runtime/`. The backend-proxied path in `channels/bus.rs` is deleted.
See Section 5 for the detailed native channel architecture.

---

## Section 1 — Rust: whole modules to delete

### 1.1  src/openhuman/billing/   (4 files)
All ops hit `/payments/*` and `/coupons/*` on the backend with a session JWT.
No replacement. Delete:
