## Section 8 — Binary files

### 8.1  src/bin/inference_probe.rs
Update the module-level doc comment that says:
  "BACKEND_URL=https://staging-api.tinyhumans.ai ..."
Replace with the fork's equivalent: configure a cloud_providers entry in config.toml.

### 8.2  src/bin/slack_backfill.rs  +  gmail_backfill_3d.rs
Both contain the string:
  "No Composio client — user not signed in (backend session) and no direct-mode ..."
Update to remove the "user not signed in (backend session)" phrase. Direct mode is the
only mode in the fork; the error should read:
  "No Composio client — set composio.api_key_provider in config.toml (direct mode)."

