## Section 9 — Execution order

Phase 1 — Delete Tier-1 modules (no cross-cutting changes needed):
  billing/, referral/, team/, openhuman_backend.rs
  Update src/openhuman/mod.rs + src/core/all.rs to remove their wiring.
  Run: cargo check --manifest-path Cargo.toml

Phase 2 — Delete socket + bus (after moving WebhookRouter):
  Move WebhookRouter to a standalone global in webhooks/.
  Delete src/openhuman/socket/, channels/bus.rs.
  Delete src/api/socket.rs.
  Update event bus startup and registration.
  Run: cargo check

Phase 3 — Clean embedded backend usage (Section 3):
  app_state/ops.rs stub, scheduler_gate simplification, doctor cleanup,
  credentials/session_support removal, config struct api_url removal,
  observability error pattern cleanup.
  Run: cargo check + cargo test

Phase 4 — Delete remaining src/api/:
  Verify zero callers with: grep -rn "crate::api" src/ | grep -v "^src/api/"
  Then delete the module.
  Run: cargo check + cargo test

Phase 5 — Embeddings + web search:
  Delete cloud embedder, update embedder factory default.
  Delete IntegrationClient, resolve web_search tool (replace or remove).
  Run: cargo check + cargo test

Phase 6 — Frontend cleanup (Section 4):
  Delete API service files, billing/team/rewards UI, update routes.
  Run: pnpm typecheck + pnpm lint

Phase 7 — Config / env / tests (Sections 6–8).

Phase 8 — Discord native write methods (Section 5.3, non-blocking improvement).

